      • getUniqueFilename

        private java.lang.String getUniqueFilename(java.lang.String suggestedExtension)
        Determine a unique filename for the resulting file.

        One paragraph may possibly contain more than one inlined picture. So we need this function to make them distinguishable.

        Parameters:
        suggestedExtension - the filename extension as it is suggested by POI
        Returns:
        the filename without a trailing dot and extension
